%% YOUR DIAGRAM HERE - Replace example below
%% =========================================
    [*] --> Initializing
    Initializing --> Operational:::operational: Sistema listo
    Operational --> Warning:::warning: Detectar problema
    Operational --> Maintenance: Mantenimiento programado
    Warning --> Error:::error: Problema crítico
    Warning --> Operational: Problema resuelto
    Error --> Recovering: Iniciar recuperación
    Recovering --> Operational: Recuperación exitosa
    Recovering --> Failed: Recuperación fallida
    Failed:::error --> [*]
    Maintenance --> Operational: Mantenimiento completo
    Operational --> Inactive:::inactive: Desactivar
    Inactive --> [*]
